{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/easiest-flex-grid-ever/","webpackCompilationHash":"","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The flexbox layout module is good news for web developers everywhere. <a href=\"http://caniuse.com/#feat=flexbox\">The part where all major browsers now support it</a> is even better news. A lot of fantastic resources, documentation and tutorials have sprung up lately. <a href=\"https://philipwalton.github.io/solved-by-flexbox/\">Solved by Flexbox</a> is one of my favorites.</p>\n<p>In the past I used very simple CSS float grids for website templating, but Flexbox is even better, and much simpler. In this quick tutorial, I will show you how to create an extremely simple, infinitely scalable responsive grid.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-demo\"><a href=\"#the-demo\" aria-label=\"the demo permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Demo</h2>\n<p>See the Pen <a href=\"http://codepen.io/taniarascia/pen/rOLEGe/\">Easiest Flex Grid Ever</a>.</p>\n<p>We have semantic options for naming the tags and classes, but I'll start off with a simple row and column based naming structure, in the vein of <a href=\"http://getbootstrap.com/css/#grid\">Bootstrap</a>, <a href=\"http://foundation.zurb.com/docs/components/grid.html\">Foundation</a>, <a href=\"http://getskeleton.com\">Skeleton</a>, and just about every other CSS framework.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note that I'm only writing about the functional code. For the examples, I've added borders and background colors to the grid to make it easier to understand.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"the-css\"><a href=\"#the-css\" aria-label=\"the css permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The CSS</h2>\n<p>With only two classes - <code class=\"language-text\">.row</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">.column</code> - we can create an infinite, equally spaced grid.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.row</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> row<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> wrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.column</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-basis</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> screen and <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">min-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 800px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.column</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/\">A Guide to Flexbox</a> by Chris Coyier explains Flexbox in detail. For this grid, we only use a few flex properties.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">display: flex</code> defines a flex container.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">flex-direction: row</code> determines the direction of each child in a flex container as left-to-right.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">flex-wrap: wrap</code> will allow a multi-line flex.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">flex-basis: 100%</code> specifies the initial main size of a flex item (100%).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I have my mobile breakpoint set to 800px. This grid can become more complicated and have more breakpoints, but I like to have just one for mobile/tablet (small screens) and one for desktop/laptop (large screens). Using <code class=\"language-text\">min-width</code> media queries is optimal for mobile first layout design.</p>\n<p>The way this is set up, each column will have 100% width on mobile, and wrap down to the next column. On desktop, all the colums will be contained to a single line.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-html\"><a href=\"#the-html\" aria-label=\"the html permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The HTML</h2>\n<p>In a framework like Bootstrap, the grid is based on 12 columns. A 50% width column would be written something like <code class=\"language-text\">col-md-6</code>. This is much simpler.</p>\n<p>First, create a row.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>row<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Inside that row, insert a column.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>row<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 100% width --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This will give you one 100% wide column. Add another column.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>row<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 50% width --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 50% width --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The width of each column is 100% divided by the number of columns within the flex container (<code class=\"language-text\">.row</code>). Predictably, adding another with divide once again.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>row<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 33.33% width --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 33.33% width --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 33.33% width --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>So far, we have equally dividing columns.</p>\n<h3 id=\"large-screen-view\"><a href=\"#large-screen-view\" aria-label=\"large screen view permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Large Screen View</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 836px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/38eff41509556ca345202166adf73061/b9380/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-4.54.32-PM.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.11961722488038%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAFCAYAAABFA8wzAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAjUlEQVQY032PywrEIBRD/f+P1IUVFbW+13eMoHScMotAam4OKfPek1KKaq1USpmCP/UvW3nvnRiAUkrKOU+llF61gOd7zmn3AGZYB+E4xvgDWceCc7outaEnHN0JdM5N4Ns6ay3hD5DdIcwSfBjeGLO/vxaiJLjYwfNACEFa670UgkeHj8X3AD6z1hp9APe4e7GgVsRsAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 4 54 32 PM\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 4 54 32 PM\"\n        src=\"/static/38eff41509556ca345202166adf73061/b9380/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-4.54.32-PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/38eff41509556ca345202166adf73061/0cb30/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-4.54.32-PM.png 213w,\n/static/38eff41509556ca345202166adf73061/a67b6/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-4.54.32-PM.png 425w,\n/static/38eff41509556ca345202166adf73061/b9380/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-4.54.32-PM.png 836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 836px) 100vw, 836px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"small-screen-view\"><a href=\"#small-screen-view\" aria-label=\"small screen view permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Small Screen View</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 769px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7babdbabee4a6972599542f54aae2811/564ac/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.21.22-PM.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.79583875162549%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAhElEQVQoz62SOwrAIBBEvf8FE1BULCyMf9R2gwMJpN4UU2zh47k7QilFpRRqrVGtlZU5JwnnHIbeO6CcAGiMAXBbcpJzpjEGiRgj7LjZhmstElKqfw1DCKBzdvi8xQ7P46Driuwrb0sYeu/f2nDy1mb3MKXEMvwArbVs4OfLWmtc6K+j3NHERWQa+OaHAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 21 22 PM\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 21 22 PM\"\n        src=\"/static/7babdbabee4a6972599542f54aae2811/564ac/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.21.22-PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7babdbabee4a6972599542f54aae2811/0cb30/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.21.22-PM.png 213w,\n/static/7babdbabee4a6972599542f54aae2811/a67b6/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.21.22-PM.png 425w,\n/static/7babdbabee4a6972599542f54aae2811/564ac/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.21.22-PM.png 769w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Also, the grid is infinitely nestable.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 850px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/796ca4fd0390417e81aab7e14afcf2b2/5648e/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.40.58-PM.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.681772406847935%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAV0lEQVQI113MQQ7AIAgEwP7/jWqM9QKi4gu2QmKT9jABshuuOSeYGDZV1UlraNu5Tb0rUkqIMXq21vrkx2VhCAEi4k9NKQU5570rxhjOeswEIkLv/e3+PZInlmyQT6+6AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 40 58 PM\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 40 58 PM\"\n        src=\"/static/796ca4fd0390417e81aab7e14afcf2b2/4d3f1/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.40.58-PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/796ca4fd0390417e81aab7e14afcf2b2/0cb30/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.40.58-PM.png 213w,\n/static/796ca4fd0390417e81aab7e14afcf2b2/a67b6/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.40.58-PM.png 425w,\n/static/796ca4fd0390417e81aab7e14afcf2b2/4d3f1/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.40.58-PM.png 850w,\n/static/796ca4fd0390417e81aab7e14afcf2b2/5648e/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.40.58-PM.png 993w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>But that's only so useful. What if you want a <a href=\"http://alistapart.com/article/holygrail\">Holy Grail</a> layout? Or a main content with a sidebar?</p>\n<p>Well, on the small screen view, it's still going to look the same - you still want each section to be full width. On desktop, it will be slightly different. Going with the Holy Grail example, say I want a main left sidebar that's 25% width, an advertisement sidebar on the right that's 20% width, and the 55% as the main content?</p>\n<p>The class names can be anything, but I'm just going to name them after the percents for simplicity.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>row<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column _25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    25% Left Sidebar\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column _55<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    55% Main Content\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column _20<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    20% Right Sidebar\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The only thing that needs to be added is the <code class=\"language-text\">flex</code> property inside of your <code class=\"language-text\">min-width</code> media query.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> screen and <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">min-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 800px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">._25</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">._55</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">._20</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"large-screen-view-1\"><a href=\"#large-screen-view-1\" aria-label=\"large screen view 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Large Screen View</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 850px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bf205fece4805d6d82937f675e1ffbc9/b47b0/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.04-PM.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.140969162995596%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAV0lEQVQI122NQQ7AIAgE/f8vFUR7qFHxvi003HqYbNhshsRMqLVizom9t6dIQ2sf0f+hqui9g5lBxLjHQCIiGGstH1iKiD8xog9BYPc55xVeKIWQc3bhA6kylraOihDxAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 32 04 PM\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 32 04 PM\"\n        src=\"/static/bf205fece4805d6d82937f675e1ffbc9/4d3f1/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.04-PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bf205fece4805d6d82937f675e1ffbc9/0cb30/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.04-PM.png 213w,\n/static/bf205fece4805d6d82937f675e1ffbc9/a67b6/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.04-PM.png 425w,\n/static/bf205fece4805d6d82937f675e1ffbc9/4d3f1/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.04-PM.png 850w,\n/static/bf205fece4805d6d82937f675e1ffbc9/b47b0/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.04-PM.png 908w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"small-screen-view-1\"><a href=\"#small-screen-view-1\" aria-label=\"small screen view 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Small Screen View</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 756px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f890a48067483bc4813d2487ab6fc20d/50bbc/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.17-PM.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27.77777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAYAAADDl76dAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAaklEQVQY06XPyQ3AIAxEUfffYBYECBFAiBCWBiYxJcSHf5mD9UwpJcQYUWvFnFMcKaWwbTu89xhjoLUmilh4l4Kc8xr4qCTSWsMYDWvt9/azxt7778g5h+sKCCGIdUt4HucnNGApvyzRcS+p5saz51FkeQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 32 17 PM\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 32 17 PM\"\n        src=\"/static/f890a48067483bc4813d2487ab6fc20d/50bbc/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.17-PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f890a48067483bc4813d2487ab6fc20d/0cb30/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.17-PM.png 213w,\n/static/f890a48067483bc4813d2487ab6fc20d/a67b6/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.17-PM.png 425w,\n/static/f890a48067483bc4813d2487ab6fc20d/50bbc/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.32.17-PM.png 756w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 756px) 100vw, 756px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Finally, you're going to want to wrap the entire grid inside of a container so your content doesn't stretch to 3000 pixels wide on an iMac.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- rows and columns --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"semantics\"><a href=\"#semantics\" aria-label=\"semantics permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Semantics</h3>\n<p>Everybody loves HTML5 semantics. Why stick with divs upon divs when we have some semantically named classes we can use instead? Rows and columns are <em>great</em> for quick template design, but once it comes down to the final code, you want something cleaner. <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element\">Read all about HTML5 semantic tags</a> if you're not overly familiar.</p>\n<h4 id=\"html\"><a href=\"#html\" aria-label=\"html permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      Article\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>aside</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      Aside\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>aside</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">main</code> is the <code class=\"language-text\">.container</code> div. The <code class=\"language-text\">main</code> tag is only meant to be used once in a document. <code class=\"language-text\">section</code> has replaced the <code class=\"language-text\">.row</code>. <code class=\"language-text\">article</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">aside</code> are two different <code class=\"language-text\">.column</code> classes.</p>\n<h4 id=\"css\"><a href=\"#css\" aria-label=\"css permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">main</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">section</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-direction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> row<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> wrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">article,\naside</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-basis</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> screen and <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">min-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 800px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">aside</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">article</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 7.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 850px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c297f53e29f321f6fb709d52a99a2a95/5648e/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.53.02-PM.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 7.854984894259818%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAOUlEQVQI12P49OnTf3Lxx48f/z9+/Pj/27fv/n/+DBFjgEmQikH6Pnz48P/u3bv/X71+DTTwM1gcAFz7mIsXpq8eAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 53 02 PM\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2015 10 07 at 5 53 02 PM\"\n        src=\"/static/c297f53e29f321f6fb709d52a99a2a95/4d3f1/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.53.02-PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c297f53e29f321f6fb709d52a99a2a95/0cb30/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.53.02-PM.png 213w,\n/static/c297f53e29f321f6fb709d52a99a2a95/a67b6/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.53.02-PM.png 425w,\n/static/c297f53e29f321f6fb709d52a99a2a95/4d3f1/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.53.02-PM.png 850w,\n/static/c297f53e29f321f6fb709d52a99a2a95/5648e/Screen-Shot-2015-10-07-at-5.53.02-PM.png 993w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>And now you have a perfectly functional, semantic layout based on flexbox!</p>","timeToRead":6,"excerpt":"The flexbox layout module is good news for web developers everywhere. The part where all major browsers now support it is even better newsâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"How to Create a Flexbox Grid","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/695197f9845f4e2da7a3da0e77e784f4/4148e/css.png","srcSet":"/static/695197f9845f4e2da7a3da0e77e784f4/4148e/css.png 1x"}}},"slug":"easiest-flex-grid-ever","date":"2015-10-07T00:00:00.000Z","categories":["Design"],"tags":["css","flex"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/easiest-flex-grid-ever/","date":"2015-10-07T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/easiest-flex-grid-ever/"}}}